- Cheers!

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.556
The method I taught you
is very relaxing, right?

00:05:49.035 --> 00:05:51.275
You grew up by the sea.

00:05:51.836 --> 00:05:53.235
How come you can't swim?

00:05:53.396 --> 00:05:55.915
