immortal either.

00:05:58.155 --> 00:05:58.996
Makes sense.

00:06:03.115 --> 00:06:04.355
When I was little,

00:06:04.756 --> 00:06:06.355
my parents were always busy with work.

00:06:07.235 --> 00:06:08.475
No one taught me to swim.

00:06:09.196 --> 00:06:10.076
Later,

00:06:10.196 --> 00:06:11.675
I lived at my grandma's house.

00:06:12.035 --> 00:06:13.196
She always told me

00:06:13.836 --> 00:06:15.996
that she'd take me to see the sea
during holidays.

00:06:16.836 --> 00:06:18.196
But when holidays came,

00:06:18.196 --> 00:06:19.516
she was always busy at the store.

00:06:21.715 --> 00:06:24.035
Later when I grew up,
I wanted to take her there,

00:06:25.996 --> 00:06:27.235
but never got the chance.

00:06:31.996 --> 00:06:32.595
Sorry.

00:06:34.595 --> 00:06:36.196
No need to apologize.

00:06:36.795 --> 00:06:37.915
Actually, when I was little,

00:06:38.836 --> 00:06:40.636
I didn't appreciate her.

00:06:42.076 --> 00:06:42.795
Why?

00:06:54.235 --> 00:06:55.475
Huang.

00:06:55.595 --> 00:06:56.275
Look.

00:06:56.275 --> 00:06:57.595
Blowing bubbles.

00:07:03.636 --> 00:07:04.436
Su Beilu.

00:07:07.396 --> 00:07:08.196
Su Beilu.

00:07:09.715 --> 00:07:10.795
What are you doing?

00:07:11.795 --> 00:07:12.956
What's in your hand?

00:07:13.436 --> 00:07:14.155
Give it to me.

00:07:15.275 --> 00:07:15.876
No.

00:07:19.115 --> 00:07:19.996
What is this?

00:07:20.556 --> 00:07:21.836
Did you take it from the store?

00:07:23.636 --> 00:07:24.795
Playing with the dog again?

00:07:25.235 --> 00:07:26.196
Wash your hands at home.

00:07:26.316 --> 00:07:26.956
Let's go.

00:07:29.076 --> 00:07:29.715
Go.

00:07:30.035 --> 00:07:31.396
I'm not going home.

00:07:31.396 --> 00:07:34.035
I need to buy watercolor pens
for tomorrow's art class.

00:07:34.595 --> 00:07:36.556
Aren't there watercolor pens
at the store?

00:07:36.595 --> 00:07:37.715
Why waste money?

00:07:37.996 --> 00:07:38.355
Go home.

00:07:38.355 --> 00:07:39.196
Grandma.

00:07:39.196 --> 00:07:40.636
Those at the store are crayons.

00:07:41.115 --> 00:07:42.595
I want watercolor pens.

00:07:42.595 --> 00:07:43.155
Let's go.

00:08:09.396 --> 00:08:10.316
Su Beilu.

00:08:10.316 --> 00:08:11.556
Is this your mom?

00:08:11.595 --> 00:08:12.915
This is my grandma.

00:08:13.155 --> 00:08:14.795
The color of your grandma's clothes

00:08:14.956 --> 00:08:17.196
looks like stir-fried eggplant
with scallions.

00:08:19.956 --> 00:08:21.076
What's going on?

00:08:21.196 --> 00:08:22.316
Everyone back to your seats.

00:08:23.675 --> 00:08:24.876
Long, are you done drawing?

00:08:24.876 --> 00:08:26.355
You're distracting other students.

00:08:26.355 --> 00:08:28.516
Miss, I'm just reminding Su Beilu.

00:08:28.556 --> 00:08:31.436
He didn't bring watercolor pens
as required.

00:08:31.436 --> 00:08:32.916
But you still can't distract others.

00:08:32.916 --> 00:08:33.755
Sit down.

00:08:34.156 --> 00:08:34.956
Continue drawing.

00:08:39.956 --> 00:08:42.090
It's fine. I will bring you watercolor pens
next time.

00:08:42.250 --> 00:08:43.115
Your drawing is good.

00:08:43.115 --> 00:08:43.875
Keep going.

00:08:51.475 --> 00:08:52.156
Where to put it?

00:08:54.276 --> 00:08:55.436
Here.

00:08:55.515 --> 00:08:56.715
Okay, let me see.

00:08:56.916 --> 00:08:57.595
Eight Fanta.

00:08:57.595 --> 00:08:58.875
The rest are Coke, right?

00:08:58.995 --> 00:08:59.676
Got it.

00:08:59.995 --> 00:09:00.995
Thanks.

00:09:00.995 --> 00:09:02.176
(Feng Ying Mini-Mart)

00:09:05.916 --> 00:09:07.276
Su Beilu, you're back.

00:09:08.836 --> 00:09:09.755
Su Beilu.

00:09:13.515 --> 00:09:14.395
Bei.

00:09:14.755 --> 00:09:15.635
Bei.

00:09:17.436 --> 00:09:18.235
Bei.

00:09:20.715 --> 00:09:21.515
Bei.

00:09:23.395 --> 00:09:24.276
Bei.

00:09:24.355 --> 00:09:25.556
What's wrong?

00:09:25.755 --> 00:09:27.836
If something's wrong, tell grandma.

00:09:30.276 --> 00:09:30.956
Bei.

00:09:31.115 --> 00:09:32.875
I will make you dinner,

00:09:32.875 --> 00:09:34.436
make something tasty for you.

00:09:34.755 --> 00:09:36.595
Come out later to eat.

00:09:39.796 --> 00:09:41.556
What's going on with this kid?

00:10:08.715 --> 00:10:09.875
When I was little,

00:10:10.635 --> 00:10:12.676
she sold things at the mini-mart.

00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:14.355
They were always
the oldest-looking stuff.

00:10:14.635 --> 00:10:16.836
I was always embarrassed
in front of classmates.

00:10:16.995 --> 00:10:18.475
What she picked

00:10:18.676 --> 00:10:20.556
always the most outdated items.

00:10:21.115 --> 00:10:22.956
I argued with her many times.

00:10:22.956 --> 00:10:23.875
Do you know

00:10:24.635 --> 00:10:26.995
why I was so happy
to see bubble water today?

00:10:29.076 --> 00:10:29.796
Because

00:10:32.076 --> 00:10:33.395
when I see bubble water,

00:10:33.395 --> 00:10:34.475
I think of her.

00:10:35.995 --> 00:10:37.076
She used

00:10:38.875 --> 00:10:40.595
to love selling these little things.

00:10:47.475 --> 00:10:48.956
I used to always think,

00:10:51.196 --> 00:10:53.355
if my parents were still here,

00:10:54.755 --> 00:10:57.036
there wouldn't be so many
unhappy things.

00:10:59.036 --> 00:10:59.875
But,

00:11:00.836 --> 00:11:02.316
after I secretly

00:11:03.276 --> 00:11:06.076
used Yashe to save my parents last time,

00:11:06.995 --> 00:11:08.395
I changed my mind.

00:11:11.076 --> 00:11:13.436
Actually, grandma is the one
who raised me.

00:11:15.796 --> 00:11:17.355
When I was young and clueless,

00:11:17.715 --> 00:11:18.995
I always got mad at her,

00:11:20.115 --> 00:11:21.556
always complained about her.

00:11:23.515 --> 00:11:24.796
When grown up,

00:11:25.995 --> 00:11:27.235
I became more sensible,

00:11:30.395 --> 00:11:32.156
yet had no chance to treat her well.

00:11:43.156 --> 00:11:45.395
Our life is really short.

00:11:47.355 --> 00:11:48.156
Family

00:11:49.595 --> 00:11:50.316
is often

00:11:51.156 --> 00:11:52.475
the most easily overlooked.

00:11:54.036 --> 00:11:56.875
We put it behind
many other relationships,

00:11:59.395 --> 00:12:01.316
just because it comes too easily.

00:12:05.196 --> 00:12:06.235
But

00:12:06.916 --> 00:12:08.715
as the days go by,

00:12:10.196 --> 00:12:12.355
we selectively block

00:12:12.916 --> 00:12:14.036
or even forget

00:12:15.156 --> 00:12:16.156
the pain,

00:12:17.036 --> 00:12:17.755
sorrow,

00:12:18.515 --> 00:12:19.916
and loss.

00:12:21.916 --> 00:12:23.635
Leaving only beautiful memories.

00:12:25.700 --> 00:12:27.556
Just like the bubble water
at grandma's store.

00:12:27.556 --> 00:12:32.496
♪The fairy tale I held so tight slips
through my fingers like sand♪

00:12:35.096 --> 00:12:38.616
♪Time, oh time, can we pause the time?♪

00:12:39.196 --> 00:12:40.276
Do you have a wish?

00:12:45.690 --> 00:12:46.956
Even if I say it, it's useless.

00:12:47.115 --> 00:12:47.715
Why?

00:12:47.715 --> 00:12:48.715
Say it.

00:12:50.416 --> 00:12:54.136
♪We said we'd grow up,
I showed up right on time♪

00:12:56.715 --> 00:12:58.475
If only I could cherish

00:12:58.475 --> 00:13:00.156
the time with grandma,

00:13:03.715 --> 00:13:05.755
maybe there wouldn't be so many regrets.

00:13:10.595 --> 00:13:11.156
But

00:13:11.836 --> 00:13:13.595
I feel very fortunate to meet

00:13:14.595 --> 00:13:15.875
such a good boss like you.

00:13:16.956 --> 00:13:19.276
I think it must be grandma blessing me.

00:13:22.556 --> 00:13:23.916
It definitely must be.

00:13:24.635 --> 00:13:25.515
What about you?

00:13:25.515 --> 00:13:26.475
Do you have a wish?

00:13:27.475 --> 00:13:28.316
I

00:13:30.115 --> 00:13:31.115
don't have one.

00:13:31.355 --> 00:13:32.156
Impossible.

00:13:32.475 --> 00:13:33.755
How can someone have no wishes?

00:13:34.156 --> 00:13:35.036
Really don't have any.

00:13:36.635 --> 00:13:38.956
Recovering lost artifacts
from different eras

00:13:39.715 --> 00:13:40.836
is my greatest wish.

00:13:44.355 --> 00:13:44.995
Alright then.

00:13:46.196 --> 00:13:47.635
Maybe after you

00:13:47.635 --> 00:13:49.395
complete this wish,

00:13:49.595 --> 00:13:50.916
you can think of the next one.

00:13:51.196 --> 00:13:52.836
Just like I come up with a new wish

00:13:53.595 --> 00:13:55.715
every year on my birthday.

00:13:59.956 --> 00:14:00.796
So,

00:14:01.076 --> 00:14:02.156
think now.

00:14:02.436 --> 00:14:04.076
What your next wish is?

00:14:04.076 --> 00:14:09.096
♪Let the waves that left
and came back wash over my feet again♪

00:14:09.936 --> 00:14:13.656
♪We said we'd grow up,
I showed up right on time♪

00:14:13.656 --> 00:14:17.496
♪Knowing it would hurt, I still set out♪

00:14:17.595 --> 00:14:18.875
I actually thought of one.

00:14:19.916 --> 00:14:20.556
What is it?

00:14:22.276 --> 00:14:23.635
If I say it, it won't work.

00:14:26.635 --> 00:14:28.556
Will you tell the wishes

00:14:28.635 --> 00:14:29.796
you make on your birthday?

00:14:31.676 --> 00:14:32.436
Exactly.

00:14:49.755 --> 00:14:50.395
Let's go.

00:14:50.995 --> 00:14:51.635
Thanks.

00:15:18.995 --> 00:15:19.635
Go, Tuanzi.

00:15:20.556 --> 00:15:21.595
Miss Lin Zhong.

00:15:21.875 --> 00:15:23.196
(Lin Zhong Guesthouse)
We'll come again next time.

00:15:23.355 --> 00:15:24.395
Always welcome.

00:15:24.755 --> 00:15:25.875
Come again?

00:15:26.076 --> 00:15:27.755
I didn't sleep well last night.

00:15:27.875 --> 00:15:28.916
Still didn't sleep well?

00:15:28.916 --> 00:15:30.115
The snoring was so loud.

00:15:30.115 --> 00:15:31.156
Impossible.

00:15:31.395 --> 00:15:33.676
Your mattress isn't good.

00:15:33.676 --> 00:15:35.676
Next time I'll recommend a good one.

00:15:35.875 --> 00:15:37.755
Thanks, no need.

00:15:39.115 --> 00:15:39.635
Oh right.

00:15:39.635 --> 00:15:42.196
Last night I painted a picture
as a gift for everyone.

00:15:42.196 --> 00:15:42.995
Let me see.

00:15:43.570 --> 00:15:45.115
Miss Lin Zhong, when did you paint this?

00:15:45.115 --> 00:15:45.956
Amazing.

00:15:45.956 --> 00:15:46.635
So cute.

00:15:46.635 --> 00:15:47.316
Miss Lin Zhong.

00:15:47.316 --> 00:15:49.436
You're secretly a recluse artist,
aren't you?

00:15:49.595 --> 00:15:50.235
How is it?

00:15:50.556 --> 00:15:51.715
The scene is lively.

00:15:51.796 --> 00:15:52.995
Colors are bold.

00:15:52.995 --> 00:15:53.520
Professional.

00:15:54.796 --> 00:15:55.355
Master Dong.

00:15:55.436 --> 00:15:56.156
Look.

00:15:56.156 --> 00:15:56.836
Like it?

00:15:58.156 --> 00:15:59.755
I agree with everything else.

00:15:59.836 --> 00:16:01.355
What do you mean by this?

00:16:01.355 --> 00:16:02.956
I'm just recording it truthfully.

00:16:02.956 --> 00:16:05.076
You drank too much last night.
Yes, that's true.

00:16:05.076 --> 00:16:05.755
Impossible.

00:16:05.875 --> 00:16:08.436
I've never gotten drunk
since I learned to drink.

00:16:09.900 --> 00:16:12.156
- We're leaving, Miss Lin Zhong.
- Bye, Miss Lin Zhong.

00:16:12.156 --> 00:16:12.875
Bye.

00:16:14.515 --> 00:16:17.036
If I were really drunk,
could I drive today?

00:16:17.715 --> 00:16:19.076
See how energetic I am now.

00:16:19.076 --> 00:16:19.755
Right?

00:16:19.956 --> 00:16:20.515
Yes.

00:16:21.755 --> 00:16:22.475
Let's go.

00:16:22.676 --> 00:16:23.196
Bye.

00:16:23.316 --> 00:16:24.796
Bye.

00:16:24.796 --> 00:16:25.956
Let's go.

00:16:40.235 --> 00:16:42.956
Good times are always short.

00:16:43.276 --> 00:16:45.316
Tomorrow we go back to work.

00:16:48.235 --> 00:16:48.956
What now?

00:16:49.595 --> 00:16:50.475
I'll see you home.

00:16:54.595 --> 00:16:55.475
Let's go to Yashe.

00:16:56.715 --> 00:16:57.436
Okay.

00:17:01.635 --> 00:17:03.395
You still have to work overtime today?

00:17:05.276 --> 00:17:07.155
I was worried I had nothing to do.

00:17:07.635 --> 00:17:09.955
Can you help me take Tuanzi home later?

00:17:12.996 --> 00:17:13.915
I sympathize with you.

00:18:09.915 --> 00:18:11.195
Before the team-building,

00:18:12.635 --> 00:18:14.476
I cleaned everything here.

00:18:15.675 --> 00:18:16.635
Just thinking

00:18:17.756 --> 00:18:20.155
it'll still be clean when I return.

00:18:32.076 --> 00:18:32.955
Su Beilu.

00:18:32.955 --> 00:18:34.516
You're leaving, right?

00:18:44.716 --> 00:18:46.076
All the artifacts are collected.

00:18:47.955 --> 00:18:48.756
Right?

00:18:53.036 --> 00:18:54.276
Without your help,

00:18:55.036 --> 00:18:57.716
I couldn't have collected
all these artifacts so quickly.

00:18:59.556 --> 00:19:00.355
Thank you.

00:19:06.195 --> 00:19:07.435
Congratulations, Bizhi.

00:19:09.316 --> 00:19:10.955
You've completed your wish.

00:19:20.236 --> 00:19:21.435
This team-building trip

00:19:22.756 --> 00:19:24.595
is a gift I give to you.

00:19:25.996 --> 00:19:26.796
How about it?

00:19:27.435 --> 00:19:28.316
Happy?

00:19:39.435 --> 00:19:40.195
Yes.

00:19:49.996 --> 00:19:52.435
I remember you described the future
to me.

00:19:57.076 --> 00:19:58.716
You said it's cold there

00:20:01.036 --> 00:20:02.395
and it makes you unhappy.

00:20:03.516 --> 00:20:04.556
I hope

00:20:05.716 --> 00:20:07.635
our memories from this time

00:20:09.996 --> 00:20:11.355
can make you

00:20:12.316 --> 00:20:13.476
smile more in the future.

00:20:15.155 --> 00:20:16.155
I also hope

00:20:16.955 --> 00:20:18.516
you will always remember

00:20:19.395 --> 00:20:21.236
these friends from the 21st century.

00:20:25.516 --> 00:20:26.595
I will definitely remember.

00:20:28.076 --> 00:20:29.155
I'll remember Chun Ge,

00:20:29.276 --> 00:20:30.076
Xiaomin,

00:20:30.395 --> 00:20:31.155
Master Dong

00:20:31.556 --> 00:20:32.915
and you, Su Beilu.

00:20:35.076 --> 00:20:36.716
Remember these good friends.

00:20:37.675 --> 00:20:38.756
Remember this era.

00:20:40.996 --> 00:20:42.115
Remember to smile more.

00:20:54.236 --> 00:20:55.675
Check it when you get home.

