00:29:06.595 --> 00:29:07.556
Come, Su.

00:29:07.556 --> 00:29:08.595
Come inside quickly.

00:29:08.595 --> 00:29:09.716
Look at this room.

00:29:09.716 --> 00:29:10.875
The furniture and decor

00:29:12.155 --> 00:29:13.595
are still the same.

00:29:19.836 --> 00:29:21.595
These little decorations are quite nice.

00:29:21.595 --> 00:29:23.036
- Miss Jenny, let me.
- Don't move.

00:29:23.635 --> 00:29:24.435
Miss Jenny.

00:29:25.036 --> 00:29:26.236
Thank you for letting me stay.

00:29:26.756 --> 00:29:28.435
I was worried about the house.

00:29:29.036 --> 00:29:30.996
Look at you, what are you saying?

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:32.620
A good neighbor is better
than a brother far off.

00:29:32.635 --> 00:29:33.355
People's hearts

00:29:33.355 --> 00:29:34.516
are made of flesh.

00:29:35.516 --> 00:29:36.276
But

00:29:36.915 --> 00:29:38.316
you're really not raising the rent?

00:29:38.915 --> 00:29:40.115
And let me keep Tuanzi.

00:29:41.690 --> 00:29:42.996
It's called Little Tuanzi, right?

00:29:43.635 --> 00:29:45.875
How is Little Tuanzi so cute?

00:29:46.996 --> 00:29:49.875
Little Tuanzi is getting cuter
and cuter.

00:29:49.875 --> 00:29:51.476
I have to leave now.

00:29:51.476 --> 00:29:52.875
Call me if you need anything.

00:29:53.130 --> 00:29:53.996
Alright, I'll go then.

00:29:53.996 --> 00:29:55.516
- Miss Jenny, I'll see you off.
- No need.

00:29:55.516 --> 00:29:56.355
Stay.

00:29:57.036 --> 00:29:57.435
Stay.

00:29:57.435 --> 00:29:58.595
Goodbye, Miss Jenny.

00:30:02.155 --> 00:30:03.316
Can't even sell it.

00:30:03.716 --> 00:30:05.915
I can't handle it if it's vacant
for a few more months.

00:30:26.316 --> 00:30:26.756
Release.

00:31:23.836 --> 00:31:25.195
Here. I'll give you the cat.

00:31:25.195 --> 00:31:26.355
Sorry about that.

00:31:26.355 --> 00:31:27.155
Wait a bit.

00:31:27.155 --> 00:31:27.595
Wait.

00:31:27.595 --> 00:31:28.836
It's too crowded now.

00:31:30.915 --> 00:31:31.556
Dr. Tang.

00:31:32.155 --> 00:31:33.435
It's really too busy.

00:31:33.435 --> 00:31:34.036
I really...

00:31:34.036 --> 00:31:34.996
I'll go get busy.

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:37.516
Dr. Tang. I just happen
to have something to tell you. Come.

00:31:37.836 --> 00:31:38.316
Go ahead.

00:31:38.476 --> 00:31:39.635
Isn't it now

00:31:40.290 --> 00:31:41.155
busier with patients?

00:31:41.155 --> 00:31:42.195
Dr. Tang!

00:31:42.200 --> 00:31:44.516
Miss Chen asked if you could see
her dog first since she's in a hurry?

00:31:44.520 --> 00:31:46.435
That won't do. Look at
how many patients there are.

00:31:46.435 --> 00:31:47.595
Let her wait a bit more.

00:31:47.595 --> 00:31:48.236
I'll tell her.

00:31:48.236 --> 00:31:49.395
Okay, go ahead.

00:31:49.836 --> 00:31:51.635
I just want to discuss with you.

00:31:51.635 --> 00:31:52.716
Discuss what? Go ahead.

00:31:52.716 --> 00:31:53.435
Dr. Tang.

00:31:53.930 --> 00:31:55.435
Has Keke's prescription been written?

00:31:55.435 --> 00:31:56.540
Should I take the medicine to him?

00:31:56.556 --> 00:31:57.996
It's been done. Go help him get it.

00:31:57.996 --> 00:31:59.476
I really don't have time. Go ahead.

00:31:59.476 --> 00:31:59.836
Alright.

00:31:59.836 --> 00:32:00.355
Xiaomin.

00:32:00.476 --> 00:32:02.195
Don't come back until I finish talking.

00:32:05.716 --> 00:32:08.036
Just see if it can be reversed.

00:32:10.996 --> 00:32:11.875
Are you okay, manager?

00:32:12.756 --> 00:32:13.996
What are you doing again?

00:32:14.115 --> 00:32:14.756
Just so.

00:32:14.756 --> 00:32:15.796
I can tell you something.

00:32:16.476 --> 00:32:17.756
I really can't keep up.

00:32:17.915 --> 00:32:20.236
Spring is the peak season
for cat and dog illnesses.

00:32:20.395 --> 00:32:22.635
The inpatient ward is full,
not to mention the ER.

00:32:22.650 --> 00:32:24.476
We're so busy we don't even
have time to eat.

00:32:24.500 --> 00:32:26.355
Ask Dr. Tang how many extra shifts
he's worked?

00:32:26.355 --> 00:32:28.756
- I've been at it for seven days.
- Yeah. Alright.

00:32:28.760 --> 00:32:30.290
You guys are busy. I'm not busy, right?

00:32:30.435 --> 00:32:31.516
I don't understand you guys.

00:32:31.516 --> 00:32:33.635
Wasn't I trying to hire people
but couldn't?

00:32:33.635 --> 00:32:35.076
Aren't you pressuring me?

00:32:35.370 --> 00:32:36.516
Am I not having a hard time?

00:32:36.520 --> 00:32:38.076
You walked off
before I finished talking.

00:32:38.076 --> 00:32:39.955
- Do you respect me?
- Manager.

00:32:39.955 --> 00:32:42.036
What exactly do you want to tell me?

00:32:44.875 --> 00:32:46.355
Think it through and then tell me.

00:32:49.155 --> 00:32:50.556
Every day is so exhausting.

00:32:50.556 --> 00:32:52.195
When will it ever end?

00:32:53.155 --> 00:32:55.355
Is the manager seriously recruiting?

00:32:55.476 --> 00:32:56.716
Where are the people?

00:32:57.556 --> 00:32:58.716
You two young ones.

00:32:58.716 --> 00:33:00.836
What's going on with you guys?

00:33:01.836 --> 00:33:02.796
Look at me.

00:33:03.635 --> 00:33:05.476
I can't hold on either.

00:33:06.276 --> 00:33:08.395
They say vet salaries are high.

00:33:08.395 --> 00:33:10.875
But only those who suffer know
how hard it is.

00:33:11.316 --> 00:33:12.115
Dr. Tang.

00:33:12.675 --> 00:33:13.915
Why don't you take a break?

00:33:14.236 --> 00:33:16.036
Or I can get you something to eat.

00:33:16.836 --> 00:33:17.675
Thanks.

00:33:17.955 --> 00:33:19.595
I just want to sit here for a bit.

00:33:19.756 --> 00:33:21.595
I still need to read some scans.

00:33:22.236 --> 00:33:23.675
I haven't finished reading my scans.

00:33:25.236 --> 00:33:26.756
Delicious luosifen has arrived.

00:33:26.955 --> 00:33:27.595
Yes.

00:33:28.030 --> 00:33:29.556
I forgot I had an appointment with you.

00:33:30.476 --> 00:33:31.556
I haven't finished work yet.

00:33:31.600 --> 00:33:32.675
You can wait for me a bit.

00:33:33.076 --> 00:33:34.450
It's fine. It's the season change.

00:33:34.476 --> 00:33:35.276
I know you're busy.

00:33:35.476 --> 00:33:36.516
So I brought you Luosifen

00:33:36.516 --> 00:33:39.875
with less spicy,
less smelly, and extra veggies.

00:33:39.875 --> 00:33:40.675
Come and eat.

00:33:40.675 --> 00:33:41.595
Good kid.

00:33:41.595 --> 00:33:42.716
You know I like this.

00:33:43.195 --> 00:33:44.036
Master is here.

00:33:44.316 --> 00:33:45.195
Master is here.

00:33:47.756 --> 00:33:48.836
It's still hot.

00:33:49.155 --> 00:33:50.756
This is too happy.

00:33:51.115 --> 00:33:51.796
So good.

00:33:51.796 --> 00:33:52.276
Thank you,

00:33:52.276 --> 00:33:52.955
Su Beilu.

00:33:54.036 --> 00:33:55.355
Where have you been lately?

00:33:55.570 --> 00:33:56.915
Haven't seen you for a long time.

00:34:00.316 --> 00:34:02.115
I've been busy moving.

00:34:02.716 --> 00:34:03.435
Moving?

00:34:03.996 --> 00:34:04.716
Why?

00:34:07.995 --> 00:34:09.236
The boss left.

00:34:09.676 --> 00:34:11.875
I feel uncomfortable living alone

00:34:12.035 --> 00:34:13.515
in such a big house.

00:34:14.035 --> 00:34:17.116
So I told the landlord
I want to move out.

00:34:17.510 --> 00:34:19.395
Didn't we just have a team-building
with him?

00:34:20.156 --> 00:34:21.236
Where did he go?

00:34:23.836 --> 00:34:24.756
Back to his hometown.

00:34:27.355 --> 00:34:28.395
Business is hard.

00:34:28.756 --> 00:34:30.475
I think the boss is actually quite nice.

00:34:30.836 --> 00:34:31.796
Will he come back?

00:34:36.316 --> 00:34:37.316
So it seems

00:34:38.515 --> 00:34:40.156
you're unemployed.

00:34:42.515 --> 00:34:43.636
Sort of.

00:34:48.555 --> 00:34:50.555
- That's great!
- That's great!

00:34:52.756 --> 00:34:53.555
No.

00:34:53.636 --> 00:34:55.796
We really aren't kicking you
when you're down.

00:34:56.316 --> 00:34:58.156
It's just too busy.

00:34:58.156 --> 00:34:59.995
So just come back to work quickly.

00:34:59.995 --> 00:35:01.990
I don't want to work overtime
anymore. Hurry back.

00:35:02.035 --> 00:35:04.236
But I caused such big trouble before

00:35:04.276 --> 00:35:05.596
and I'm always clumsy.

00:35:05.596 --> 00:35:06.316
Failed exams too.

00:35:06.316 --> 00:35:07.716
Don't talk about useless things.

00:35:07.716 --> 00:35:08.596
Just tell me.

00:35:08.875 --> 00:35:10.515
Do you like this profession?

00:35:10.796 --> 00:35:11.636
Yes.

00:35:11.836 --> 00:35:12.796
Then that's it.

00:35:13.075 --> 00:35:14.156
Listen.

00:35:14.515 --> 00:35:15.395
Being a vet,

00:35:15.555 --> 00:35:16.636
the important thing

00:35:16.636 --> 00:35:18.116
is to have a...

00:35:18.475 --> 00:35:20.236
- Pure heart!
- Pure heart!

00:35:20.676 --> 00:35:21.276
Don't worry.

00:35:21.276 --> 00:35:23.156
I'll talk to the manager.

00:35:23.156 --> 00:35:25.156
You just keep your distance.

00:35:25.276 --> 00:35:26.236
Focus on your own work.

00:35:26.236 --> 00:35:27.035
Steadily.

00:35:28.995 --> 00:35:29.836
Master.

00:35:30.316 --> 00:35:32.196
I'll go talk to him myself.

00:35:32.515 --> 00:35:34.995
After all, I caused such
big trouble before.

00:35:35.196 --> 00:35:36.395
I want to resolve it myself.

00:35:36.636 --> 00:35:37.555
No problem.

00:35:37.636 --> 00:35:39.890
I said not to prescribe this medicine,
there's no stock!

00:35:40.236 --> 00:35:41.955
Haven't I already signed this?

00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:42.875
Why is it here again?

00:35:42.915 --> 00:35:43.995
Who is it?

00:35:45.316 --> 00:35:46.280
What are you doing here?

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:48.236
Manager. I have something
to discuss with you.

00:35:48.676 --> 00:35:49.955
Manager, also this.

00:35:50.196 --> 00:35:52.716
Can't you just handle
these small matters yourselves?

00:35:52.716 --> 00:35:53.995
It must be signed today.

00:35:56.756 --> 00:35:57.596
So fierce.

00:36:01.676 --> 00:36:03.875
I heard you've been
short-staffed recently.

00:36:04.035 --> 00:36:04.676
Stop.

00:36:06.000 --> 00:36:07.796
Last time you left,
you were pretty arrogant.

00:36:08.836 --> 00:36:10.116
Our clinic is too small,

00:36:10.116 --> 00:36:11.555
it can't fit someone like you.

00:36:11.915 --> 00:36:13.130
Can you give me another chance?

00:36:13.140 --> 00:36:15.090
I really want to come back
and continue working.

00:36:15.276 --> 00:36:16.035
I beg you.

00:36:16.035 --> 00:36:16.875
I'm so busy now.

00:36:16.875 --> 00:36:19.316
I really don't have the energy
to argue with you.

00:36:19.756 --> 00:36:21.236
With your stubborn personality,

00:36:21.236 --> 00:36:23.716
being a small assistant
would really be beneath you.

00:36:23.716 --> 00:36:25.555
Please find
a better opportunity elsewhere.

00:36:32.910 --> 00:36:34.756
Still not leaving?
Should I ask you to leave?

00:36:34.796 --> 00:36:35.236
Zhuang.

00:36:35.236 --> 00:36:35.836
Manager.

00:36:36.035 --> 00:36:37.035
Listen to me.

00:36:37.355 --> 00:36:39.035
I wasn't diligent enough before

00:36:39.555 --> 00:36:40.756
and I was always late.

00:36:41.156 --> 00:36:42.676
I kept failing the license exam.

00:36:43.355 --> 00:36:44.116
But

00:36:45.435 --> 00:36:47.756
I really love being with animals,

00:36:48.756 --> 00:36:50.955
helping them gives me a sense
of accomplishment.

00:36:52.515 --> 00:36:54.756
Before, I didn't know how
to cherish this job.

00:36:55.475 --> 00:36:56.995
But I met a friend.

00:36:57.515 --> 00:36:58.475
He told me

00:37:00.116 --> 00:37:01.480
that one must take responsibility.

00:37:01.995 --> 00:37:03.156
I have to bear

00:37:03.276 --> 00:37:04.756
my own duties.

00:37:06.196 --> 00:37:06.995
So

00:37:10.716 --> 00:37:12.756
can you reconsider

00:37:13.596 --> 00:37:14.875
and give me another chance?

00:37:15.836 --> 00:37:17.196
I will work hard.

00:37:24.915 --> 00:37:26.035
Su Beilu.

00:37:26.875 --> 00:37:28.236
I've been waiting for today.

